{"title_page": "Pranjal Bhatt", "text_new": "<!-- Please do not remove or change this AfD message until the discussion has been closed. -->\n{{Article for deletion/dated|page=Pranjal Bhatt|timestamp=20200410130834|year=2020|month=April|day=10|substed=yes|help=off}}\n<!-- Once discussion is closed, please place on talk page: {{Old AfD multi|page=Pranjal Bhatt|date=10 April 2020|result='''keep'''}} -->\n<!-- End of AfD message, feel free to edit beyond this point -->\n{{External links|date=September 2019}}\n{{short description|Indian actress and model}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = \n}}\n\n'''Pranjal Bhatt''' (\u0aaa\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0a82\u0a9c\u0ab2 \u0aad\u0a9f\u0acd\u0a9f) is an Indian [[Gujarati cinema|Gujarati film]] actress and model. Pranjal won her first film award at the age of 17<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.divyabhaskar.co.in/news/100313030159_pranjal_bhatt_got_transmedia_award.html|title=\u0aaa\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0a82\u0a9c\u0ab2 \u0aad\u0a9f\u0acd\u0a9f\u0aa8\u0ac7 \u0ab6\u0acd\u0ab0\u0ac7\u0ab7\u0acd\u0aa0 \u0a85\u0aad\u0abf\u0aa8\u0ac7\u0aa4\u0acd\u0ab0\u0ac0\u0aa8\u0acb \u0a9f\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0aa8\u0acd\u0ab8\u0aae\u0ac0\u0aa1\u0abf\u0aaf\u0abe \u0a8f\u0ab5\u0acb\u0ab0\u0acd\u0aa1 \u0a8f\u0aa8\u0abe\u0aaf\u0aa4|date=2010-03-13|website=divyabhaskar|language=gujarati|access-date=2019-05-23}}</ref> and has played a leading role in several Gujarati movies.{{Incomplete list|date=April 2020}}\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[https://www.imdb.com/name/nm7048184/?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm Pranjal Bhatt] on IMDb\n\n[[Category:Actresses from Ahmedabad]]\n[[Category:Models from Gujarat]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "text_old": "<!-- Please do not remove or change this AfD message until the discussion has been closed. -->\n{{Article for deletion/dated|page=Pranjal Bhatt|timestamp=20200410130834|year=2020|month=April|day=10|substed=yes|help=off}}\n<!-- Once discussion is closed, please place on talk page: {{Old AfD multi|page=Pranjal Bhatt|date=10 April 2020|result='''keep'''}} -->\n<!-- End of AfD message, feel free to edit beyond this point -->\n{{External links|date=September 2019}}\n{{short description|Indian actress and model}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Pranjal Bhatt\n| image              = PranjalBhatt GujaratGovAward cropped.jpg\n| caption            = Pranjal Bhatt in 2013\n| birth_place        = [[Ahmedabad]], [[India]]\n| residence          = [[Ahmedabad]], [[India]]\n| citizenship        = Indian\n| occupation         = {{flat list|\n* Actress\n* Producer\n* Model\n* Philanthropist\n}}\n| yearsactive        = 1998\u2013present\n}}\n\n'''Pranjal Bhatt''' (\u0aaa\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0a82\u0a9c\u0ab2 \u0aad\u0a9f\u0acd\u0a9f) is an Indian [[Gujarati cinema|Gujarati film]] actress and model. Pranjal won her first film award at the age of 17<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.divyabhaskar.co.in/news/100313030159_pranjal_bhatt_got_transmedia_award.html|title=\u0aaa\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0a82\u0a9c\u0ab2 \u0aad\u0a9f\u0acd\u0a9f\u0aa8\u0ac7 \u0ab6\u0acd\u0ab0\u0ac7\u0ab7\u0acd\u0aa0 \u0a85\u0aad\u0abf\u0aa8\u0ac7\u0aa4\u0acd\u0ab0\u0ac0\u0aa8\u0acb \u0a9f\u0acd\u0ab0\u0abe\u0aa8\u0acd\u0ab8\u0aae\u0ac0\u0aa1\u0abf\u0aaf\u0abe \u0a8f\u0ab5\u0acb\u0ab0\u0acd\u0aa1 \u0a8f\u0aa8\u0abe\u0aaf\u0aa4|date=2010-03-13|website=divyabhaskar|language=gujarati|access-date=2019-05-23}}</ref> and has played a leading role in several Gujarati movies.\n\n=== Awards ===\n[[File:PranjalBhatt GujaratGovAward.jpg|border|thumb|Pranjal at Government of Gujarat Award for best actress of the year 2009.]]\nPranjal Bhatt won the Transmedia Award for Best Actress of the Year in 2013<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.musicunplugged.in/news/trade_news_info/72/490|title=Musicunplugged.in : news|last=Ferreira|first=Verus|website=www.musicunplugged.in|language=en|access-date=2019-05-23}}</ref>. She has received an award from the Government of Gujarat State for her performance with the film \"Mota Ghar Ni Vahu\" for the year 2009.\n\n=== Filmography ===\n{{Incomplete list|date=April 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+\n!Film\n!Year\n!Language\n!Role\n!Director\n!Notes\n!Reference\n|-\n|''Preet Janmo Janam Ni Bhulashe Nahi''\n|2009\n|[[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]\n|Janki (Lead actress)\n|Atmaram Thakor\n|Pranjal Received best actress Transmedia Screen and Stage Award<ref name=\":0\" />\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gujaratifilmy.blogspot.com/2018/07/preet-janamo-janam-ni-bhulashe-nahi.html|title=gujarati kalakar: preet janamo janam ni bhulashe nahi|last=Kalakar|first=Gujarati|date=2018-07-04|website=gujarati kalakar|access-date=2019-05-14}}</ref>\n|-\n|''The End''\n|2017\n|[[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]\n|Nidhi Anjaria (lead actress)\n|Yogesh Joshi\n|\n|\n|-\n|''Patan Thi Pakistan''\n|2013\n|[[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]\n|Hina (lead actress)\n|Haresh Patel\n|Pranjal received best actress Transmedia Screen and Stage Award<ref name=\":1\" />\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Patan Thi Pakistan Movie: Showtimes, Review, Trailer, Posters, News & Videos {{!}} eTimes|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/gujarati/movie-details/patan-thi-pakistan/movieshow/61217245.cms|access-date=2019-05-14}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Shootout''\n|2016\n|[[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]\n|ACP Mirza (lead actress)\n|Shain Leuva\n|\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Shootout Movie: Showtimes, Review, Trailer, Posters, News & Videos {{!}} eTimes|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/gujarati/movie-details/shootout/movieshow/61222582.cms|access-date=2019-05-14}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Dikro Kahu ke dev''\n|2006\n|[[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]\n|Raajal\n|Atmaram Thakor\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gujaratifilm.co.in/2018/01/dikro-kahu-ke-dev.html|title=Dikro kahu ke dev|