CS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[Northern Boulevard (IND Queens Boulevard Line)|Northern Boulevard]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Queens local day|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[46th Street (IND Queens Boulevard Line)|46th Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Queens local day|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[Steinway Street (IND Queens Boulevard Line)|Steinway Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Queens local day|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[36th Street (IND Queens Boulevard Line)|36th Street/Northern Boulevard]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Queens local day|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[Queens Plaza (IND Queens Boulevard Line)|Queens Plaza]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Access icon}}\n| {{NYCS Queens Plaza|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''[[Manhattan]]'''\n|-\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''[[BMT Broadway Line|Broadway Line]]'''\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| align=center rowspan = 2 {{N/A}}\n| [[Lexington Avenue/59th Street (BMT Broadway Line)|Lexington Avenue/59th Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Broadway 60th|time=show|exclude=R}}<br />{{NYCS Lexington|time=show}} ([[IRT Lexington Avenue Line]])<br />Out-of-system transfer with [[MetroCard (New York City)|MetroCard]]: {{NYCS 63rd Lexington|time=show}} ([[63rd Street Lines]] at [[Lexington Avenue\u201363rd Street (New York City Subway)|Lexington Avenue\u201363rd Street]])\n| [[Roosevelt Island Tramway]]\n|-\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|allexceptnights}}\n| [[Fifth Avenue\u201359th Street (BMT Broadway Line)|Fifth Avenue\u201359th Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Broadway 60th|time=show|exclude=R}}\n|\n|-\n| style=\"background:grey;\" colspan=\"6\"|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" colspan=\"6\"| '''[[BMT Broadway Line|Broadway Line]]''' (Queens Boulevard and Second Avenue branches merge)\n|-\n| align=center