{"title_page": "Chromium (film)", "text_new": "{{short description|2015 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Chromium\n| image          = Chromium (film).png\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Bujar Alimani]]\n| producer       = \n| writer         = Bujar Alimani\n| starring       = [[Frefjon Ruci]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{film date|2015|7|8|[[Karlovy Vary International Film Festival|KVIFF]]|2015|10|15|Albania|df=yes}}\n| runtime        = 78 minutes\n| country        = Albania\n| language       = Albanian\n| budget         = \n}}\n\n'''''Chromium''''' ({{lang-sq|'''Krom'''}}) is a 2015 Albanian [[drama film]] directed by [[Bujar Alimani]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kviff.com/en/programme/film/3315961-chromium/ |title=Chromium |work=KVIFF |accessdate=3 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/chromium-krom-933317 |title='Chromium' ('Krom'): Film Review |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=3 November 2018}}</ref> It was selected as the Albanian entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[89th Academy Awards]] but it was not nominated.<ref name=\"Albania\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-albania-selects-chromium-foreign-929983 |title=Oscars: Albania Selects 'Chromium' for Foreign-Language Category |first=Nick |last=Holdsworth |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=18 September 2016 |accessdate=18 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Frefjon Ruci]]\n* [[Klodjana Keco]]\n* [[Mirela Naska]]\n* [[Kasem Hoxha]]\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of submissions to the 89th Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n* [[List of Albanian submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|4957492|Chromium}}\n\n{{Albanian submission for Academy Awards}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Chromium}}\n[[Category:2015 films]]\n[[Category:2015 drama films]]\n[[Category:Albanian films]]\n[[Category:Albanian drama films]]\n[[Category:Albanian-language films]]\n{{Albania-film-stub}}\n{{2010s-drama-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2015 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2017}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Chromium\n| image          = Chromium (film).png\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Bujar Alimani]]\n| producer       = \n| writer         = Bujar Alimani\n| starring       = [[Frefjon Ruci]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{film date|2015|7|8|[[Karlovy Vary International Film Festival|KVIFF]]|2015|10|15|Albania|df=yes}}\n| runtime        = 78 minutes\n| country        = Albania\n| language       = Albanian\n| budget         = \n}}\n\n'''''Chromium''''' ({{lang-sq|'''Krom'''}}) is a 2015 Albanian [[drama film]] directed by [[Bujar Alimani]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kviff.com/en/programme/film/3315961-chromium/ |title=Chromium |work=KVIFF |accessdate=3 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/chromium-krom-933317 |title='Chromium' ('Krom'): Film Review |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=3 November 2018}}</ref> It was selected as the Albanian entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[89th Academy Awards]] but it was not nominated.<ref name=\"Albania\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-albania-selects-chromium-foreign-929983 |title=Oscars: Albania Selects 'Chromium' for Foreign-Language Category |first=Nick |last=Holdsworth |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=18 September 2016 |accessdate=18 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Frefjon Ruci]]\n* [[Klodjana Keco]]\n* [[Mirela Naska]]\n* [[Kasem Hoxha]]\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of submissions to the 89th Aca